Perrotin is pleased to present Bauhaus Gal â€“ Theatre , Chen Keâ€™s first solo exhibition at Paris gallery. For this new exhibition, the artist created a series of portraits of young Bauhaus students and architectural photographs presented in a theatrical scenography.
